-- Vale Sells $1 Billion of Bonds Maturing in 2022
-- B y   A d r i a n a   C h i a r i n i
-- 2012-01-04T23:06:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-04/vale-sells-1-billion-of-bonds-maturing-in-2022.html
Vale SA (VALE3)  sold $1 billion of bonds
maturing in 2022, according to an e-mailed statement.  The securities have a coupon of 4.375 percent and were
priced with a spread of 255 basis points over U.S. Treasuries,
Vale said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Adriana Chiarini in Rio de Janeiro at 
 achiarini4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
